                        Liao, H., Joshi, A., & Chuang, A., 2004, Sticking out like a sore thumb: Employee dissimilarity and deviance at work                        , Personnel Psychology                        , Vol.57                                                , Pages 969 - 1000                        , (SSCI impact factor = 4.540)(科技部組織與管理領域第一級學術期刊)                        , ( SSCI )                                                    


                        Liao, H., & Chuang, A., 2004, A multilevel investigation of factors influencing employee service performance and customer outcomes                        , Academy of Management Journal                        , Vol.47                        , No.1                        , Pages 41 - 58                        , (SSCI impact factor = 6.483)((Best doctoral paper award in Organizational Behavior/Organization Theory/Organizational Development track of the Southern Management Association, USA.獲「美國南方管理學會研討會」最佳博士生學術論文獎)(科技部組織與管理領域第一級學術期刊)                        , ( SSCI )                                                    


                        Chuang, A., 2001, The perceived importance of person-job fit and person-organization fit between and within interview stages                        , Doctoral dissertation, University of Minnesota, Minneapolis                                                                                                                                                                    





